Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的耳朵红了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这证明你撒了谎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是让三笠帮忙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…爸爸要出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去内地给人看病
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要花上两三天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦说他想进调查兵团
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三笠  我不是让你不要说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟在想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道去到墙外的人究竟死了多少吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么想去墙外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道墙外的世界是什么样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.38,0:13:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要这样一无所知地在墙内度过一生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,墙内要是没有人愿意继续调查的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今死去的人们的血岂不是白流了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公等等  快说服艾伦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔菈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.99,0:14:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类的好奇心可不是被人说上一两句就会平息的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.58,0:14:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我回来就带你去看一直被我当作秘密的地下室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈可不同意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进调查兵团这种蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然说这是蠢事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是觉得能坦然地作为家畜生活下去的人类更愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.86,0:14:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:14:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三笠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子很靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰到困难的话你们一定要互相帮助啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼  怎么啦  你这个异端
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不甘心的话就还手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会那么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就和你们一样低级了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你们觉得我说的是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有办法反驳  只能动手不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不正代表你们已经认输了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  你这个满嘴歪理的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个笨蛋  居然又送上门来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么想被痛扁一顿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我不打得你满地找牙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三…三笠也在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行  这里还是先撤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那帮家伙  看到我就吓跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:16:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  他们是看到三笠才吓跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.47,0:16:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧  阿明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己能站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说「不管怎样人类还是应当前往墙外的世界」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着就被打了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还说我是异端
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想去墙外而已  为什么就要被人翻白眼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为墙内的和平持续了百年之久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不让人们冒失地闯到墙外  把它们引到墙内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国王政权的政策是将对墙外感兴趣的想法视为禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赌上的是自己的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用得着他们来管吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  你还真敢向我父母告密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不记得有答应过要帮你保密
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们…当然很不高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实觉得坚信墙内永远太平的人们有些不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说墙在百年之间屹立不倒安然无恙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但并不能保证它今天就不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里爆炸了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么东西掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  阿明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟能看到什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.65,0:18:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那堵墙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是有50米之高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是它们…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,墙…墙上被开了一个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨人们进来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家还在那边  妈妈她还…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三笠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个城市…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:20:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上会被无数的巨人所占领
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎片不会砸中我家的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要拐过那个转角
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能看到和往常一样的家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三笠  你搬那边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这根柱子挪开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  三笠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.34,0:20:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨人进来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.68,0:20:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦  快点带上三笠逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:20:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想跑啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:21:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快点给我出来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈的腿被石块压断了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算能从这里出去也跑不动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我背着你跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么总是不听妈妈的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后了好歹听我一句啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.33,0:21:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三笠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.58,0:21:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去我们三个都会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快带上孩子们逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被你小看了我可是会很头疼的啊  卡尔菈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要宰了巨人  救下你们三人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.19,0:21:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  你不能去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实  只救两个人的话我是能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.15,0:21:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  现在正是我报恩的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.59,0:22:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  汉尼斯  你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.47,0:22:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈她还…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.39,0:22:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦  三笠  你们要活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别丢下我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.38,0:22:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.58,0:23:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天  人类回想起了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.84,0:23:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被它们所支配的恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.10,0:23:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及被囚禁在鸟笼之中的屈辱
Comment: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,======
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.94,0:25:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预告
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.86,0:25:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歇根西娜沦陷
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.11,0:25:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留给人类的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.86,0:25:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有祈祷  尖叫  以及死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.66,0:25:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而在他们中
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.41,0:25:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯有艾伦在他幼小的心灵中立下了复仇的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.47,0:25:39.93,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天\N{\fs-2}—歇根西娜的陷落{\fs-1}②—
